The paper discusses the use of robotics and autonomous systems (RAS) in the agricultural sector, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also mentions the use of digital technologies and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in the transformation of the food production process. Computer vision (cs.CV) is also mentioned as a technology that can be used in the development of agricultural robots. The paper also discusses the need for control systems (cs.SY) to ensure the safe and efficient operation of agricultural robots. Finally, the paper mentions the need for research and innovation (cs.LG) to ensure that these technologies reach their full potential in the agricultural sector.
